'''Kamal Hachkar''' (  yavutse ku ya 25 Gashyantare 1977), ni umukinnyi wa firime ukomoka muri [[Maroke]] [[Ubufaransa|n'ubufaransa]], akaba n'umuhanga .  Kamal azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa filime ''yamamaye cyane Tinghir-Yeruzalemu: The Echoes of mellah'' . 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Gashyantare 1977 i Tinghir, muri [[Maroke|Maroc]] mu muryango wa Berber.  Afite amezi atandatu gusa, yavuye muri [[Maroc]] ari kumwe na nyina yerekeza mu [[Bufaransa]], aho se yakoraga nk'umukozi kuva mu 1968. Icyakora, yagiye asura Tinghir buri gihe mu biruhuko. Kamal yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu mateka yo hagati y’isi y’abayisilamu muri kaminuza ya Sorbonne . Mu 2005, yabaye umwarimu nyuma yo gutanga icyemezo cy'ubuhanga bwo kwigisha amashuri yisumbuye.  

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2013, Kamal yakoze umushinga wa documentaire yambere, ''Tinghir-Yerusalemu: Les Échos du mellah'' .  Iyi filime yashyizweho mu gihe cyo kurinda [[Abafaransa]] muri [[Maroc]] ivuga ku buzima n’imibereho y’imiryango y’abayisilamu ya Berber n’abayahudi i Tinghir mu bihe bikomeye. Nubwo, byari ingingo itavugwaho rumwe muri [[Maroc]], yanenzwe n’abayisilamu.  Nyuma, Ishyaka ry'Ubutabera n'Iterambere naryo ryinjiye mu kunegura bavuga ko ari ubutumire bwo guhuza umubano hagati ya [[Isiraheli]]. Icyakora, iyi filime yakiriwe neza ndetse n'ibihembo byinshi mu iserukiramuco rya sinema ry’igihugu cya [[Maroc]]. 

